Comment: Logotype or icon for Customizer GUI
 .
 PNG image data, 140 x 140, 8-bit/color RGBA, non-interlaced
 .
 The logo was derived from the base image "Tools, Hammer,
 Spanner" by Andy on Openclipart, which can be found at the
 following URL
 'https://openclipart.org/detail/67/tools-hammer-spanner'
 .
 Openclipart may be used for any purpose, including
 unlimited commercial productions, as royalty-free clipart,
 for schools, churches, commercial and non-commercial
 reasons.

