Files: icons/*
Copyright: 2016 Mubiin Kimura
License: GPL-2
Comment: Refresh icons for Customizer
 .
 PNG image data, SVG Scalable Vector Graphics image
 .
 These icons were recreated from source images of logo.png
 using Inkscape vector image editor.
 .
 Provided size: 256, 128, 48, 24
 .
 Provided format: SVG, PNG
 .
 The size of 128 may be used to replace logo.png and size
 of 24 is used for authentication dialog by pkexec. 

Files: INSTALL
Copyright: 2016 Mubiin Kimura
License: GPL-2
Comment: Install script for Customizer "old stable"
 .
 Bourne-Again shell script, ASCII text executable
 .
 This will make installation easier (#141). This script shall
 be distributed with source code of Customizer. This was
 removed in last commit when "old stable" is deprecated.
